# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Tracker Modules (XM/IT) - Recommended for Music
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
#
# Tracker music is more memory-efficient than streamed audio.
# Provides adaptive music capabilities (tempo, channels).
# Use for game soundtracks when possible.

