# =============================================================================
# Optional: Asset Groups
# =============================================================================
#
# Group related assets for organizational clarity (not functional)
# This is a documentation convention, not parsed by the build tool

# Vehicles Group:
# - speedster (mesh + textures)
# - muscle (mesh + textures)
# - racer (mesh + textures)

# Environment Group:
# - building_tall (mesh + textures)
# - barrier (mesh + textures)
# - boost_pad (mesh + textures)


# =============================================================================
# Build Tool Usage
# =============================================================================
#
# Commands:
#   nether build           - Build ROM from nether.toml
#   nether build --release - Optimized release build
#   nether validate        - Validate assets against budgets
#   nether pack            - Package for distribution
#
# The build tool will:
# 1. Compile Rust code from src/
# 2. Bundle all referenced assets
# 3. Validate asset constraints
# 4. Generate .nrom file
